      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Andreas Strangmüller</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:152px;\"><a href=\"http://www.bdf-fernschachbund.de/newsletter/ausgaben/april2007.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/f/f4/Strangmueller_Andreas.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"189\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Strangmueller_Andreas.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Andreas Strangmüller <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Andreas Strangmüller</b>,<br />\na German  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Correspondence_chess\">correspondence chess</a> player and World Champion of the <i>International Email Chess Group</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> in the 2004 cycle <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. Since August 2013, Andreas Strangmüller maintains the <a href=\"/FGRL\" title=\"FGRL\">FGRL</a> computer chess <a href=\"/Engine_Rating_Lists\" title=\"Engine Rating Lists\">engine rating list</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, further conducting experiments concerning <a href=\"/Branching_Factor\" title=\"Branching Factor\">branching factor</a> and <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">engine strength</a> as function of <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">search time</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">transposition table</a> size, <a href=\"/X86-64\" title=\"X86-64\">processor type</a>, and number of <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">threads</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2013\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2014\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2014</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013\">2013</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2013\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49097\">New Rating Lists (FGRL)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 25, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49775\">Rating Lists (FGRL)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 20, 2013</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2014\">2014</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2014\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50860\">Top 3 Tournament - 30 Minutes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51655\">Threads-Test</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 18, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52021\">Playing strength development - increasing time control</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 17, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52219\">Threads-Test - SF, Zappa, Komodo - 1 vs. 2, 4, 8, 16 Threads</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Zappa\" title=\"Zappa\">Zappa</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=570955\">Threads factor: Komodo, Houdini, Stockfish and Zappa</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 17, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a>, <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Zappa\" title=\"Zappa\">Zappa</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53995\">Threads test incl. Stockfish 5 and Komodo 8</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 09, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54009\">Threads test - Stockfish 5 against Komodo 8</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 10, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54059\">Threads test incl. Crafty 24.1</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54131\">Scaling with threads based on Andreas Strangmüller tests</a> by <a href=\"/Kai_Laskos\" title=\"Kai Laskos\">Kai Laskos</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 24, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54133\">Current data - threads-nps efficiency up to 32 threads</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 24, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54928\">Komodo 8 - 5-men Syzygy tablebases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 10, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Komodo#8\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo 8</a>, <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2016</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58887\">Threads test incl. Stockfish 7</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58950\">Threads test incl. Komodo 9.3</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 17, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61784\">Doubling of time control</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 21, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics#DoublingTC\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Doubling TC</a>, <a href=\"/Depth#DiminishingReturns\" title=\"Depth\">Diminishing Returns</a>, <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a>, <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62146\">Stockfish 8 - Double time control vs. 2 threads</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  November 15, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics#DoublingTC\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Doubling TC</a>, <a href=\"/Depth#DiminishingReturns\" title=\"Depth\">Diminishing Returns</a>, <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2017</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63903\">Symmetric multiprocessing (SMP) scaling - SF8 and K10.4</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 05, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a>, <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63955\">Symmetric multiprocessing (SMP) scaling - K10.4 Contempt=0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/SMP\" title=\"SMP\">SMP</a>, <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a>, <a href=\"/Contempt_Factor\" title=\"Contempt Factor\">Contempt Factor</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63967\">Symmetric multiprocessing (SMP) scaling - SF8 Contempt=10</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 13, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/SMP\" title=\"SMP\">SMP</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Contempt_Factor\" title=\"Contempt Factor\">Contempt Factor</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2019</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://forum.computerschach.de/cgi-bin/mwf/topic_show.pl?tid=10194\">Leela Zero (Lc0) - NVIDIA Geforce RTX 2060</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Strangmüller</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CSS Forum</a>, January 29, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Strangm%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fastgm.de/\">FastGMs Rating Lists (FGRL)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sueddeutsche.de/panorama/fernschach-weltmeister-im-spiel-ergraut-1.858948\">Fernschach-Weltmeister - Im Spiel ergraut - Panorama</a> von <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.bdzv.de/preistraeger-preisverleihung/preisverleihung-2000/hans-kratzer/\">Hans Kratzer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%BCddeutsche_Zeitung\">Süddeutsche.de</a>, May 17, 2010 (German)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Stra